section#values

  a(id="values" href="#values")
    h2 values

  p When the `=` symbol follows a tag, it indicates that the value should be an
    | expression. An expression can include values from the data passed to the
    | template or any valid javascript.

  pre.input
    code.
      h1 = 'Hello, ' + name

  p Mineral detects `console.log`-like statements.
  pre.input
    code.
      h1 = 'Hello %s', foo
